   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:id="vicavNews">
             <head type="newsHeader">News</head>

             <div type="newsItem">
                 <p xml:space="preserve">
                     <hi rendition="#b">5.4.2019:</hi> Bettina Leitner has contributed a new feature list for  
                     <ref target="feature:ling_features_ahwaz/Ahwaz">Ahwaz (Iran)</ref>. 
                 </p>
             </div>             
             
             <div type="newsItem">
                 <p xml:space="preserve">
                     <hi rendition="#b">18.3.2019:</hi> Our bibliography has just gone beyond the 4000 entries mark. The 4028 bibliographic items contain 
                     6304 geo-tags and 13.045 taxonomy labels. 
                 </p>
             </div>             
             
             <div type="newsItem">
                 <p xml:space="preserve">
                     <hi rendition="#b">15.3.2019:</hi> New function to <rs ref="text:vicav_explore_features func:insertFeatureMarkers()">compare features</rs>.
                 </p>
             </div>             
             
             <div type="newsItem">
                 <p xml:space="preserve">
                     <hi rendition="#b">1.3.2019:</hi> The <rs ref="text:dictFrontPage_Baghdad">Baghdad 
                         dictionary</rs> goes online.
                 </p>
             </div>             
             
             <div type="newsItem">
                 <p xml:space="preserve"><hi rendition="#b">28.2.2019:</hi> VICAV has 41 new profiles, all in 
                     all <rs ref="text:vicavExplanationProfiles func:insertProfileMarkers()">58 profiles </rs> now!
                 </p>
             </div>
             
             <div type="newsItem">
                 <p xml:space="preserve"><hi rendition="#b">2.2.2019:</hi> The <rs ref="text:vicavExplanationBibliography">VICAV 
                     Bibliography</rs> has undergone a substantial rebuild. All the bibliographical data is now in TEI encoding, the
                     whole application now making use of TEI (P5).
                 </p>
             </div>
             
             <div type="newsItem">
                 <p xml:space="preserve"><hi rendition="#b">3.12.2018:</hi> The cross <rs ref="func:createNewCrossDictQueryPanel()">dictionary search</rs> is finished. 
                     It is now possible to query all dictionary simultaneously.
                 </p>
             </div>
         </div>

      </body>
   </text>
